                        <li><a href="#contacts">Contacts</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#social-media">Social Media</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <h1>Sports: Latest News and Events</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="sports">
            <div class="sport-item">
                <h3>Football: Limpopo Derby Results</h3>
                <p>Stay updated with the latest results from the Limpopo Derby as local football clubs compete for the top spot in the league.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-item">
                <h3>Basketball: Local League Highlights</h3>
                <p>Catch the latest action from the Limpopo basketball league, featuring exciting games and standout performances from top players.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-item">
                <h3>Rugby: Upcoming Tournaments</h3>
                <p>Get all the details on upcoming rugby tournaments in Limpopo, with exclusive interviews and team preparations leading up to the events.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-item">
                <h3>Athletics: Junior Championships</h3>
                <p>Discover the rising stars of Limpopo in athletics as the junior championships take center stage this season.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-item">
                <h3>Motorsports: Latest Updates</h3>
                <p>Explore the thrilling world of motorsports in Limpopo, featuring the latest races, results, and insights into the local racing scene.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-item">
                <h3>Cricket: Limpopo Team's Performance</h3>
                <p>Follow the Limpopo cricket team as they take on top provincial teams in their quest to secure a place in the national championships.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Seopa Media. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
